headline: Cummins Inc. Declares Quarterly Common Stock Dividend
summary: COLUMBUS, Ind., October 14, 2025--The Board of Directors of Cummins Inc. (NYSE: CMI) today declared a quarterly common stock cash dividend of 2.00 dollars per share. The dividend is payable on December 4, 2025, to shareholders of record on November 21, 2025.
